### smchk.sh usage
## Forground
$ sh smchk.sh recently_days

## Logfile
$ sh smchk.sh recently_days > filename

### Example
# Recently 35 days checking
# default recently_days = 30
$ sh smchk.sh 35 > 20211211.log
